snippet.title: #IStandWithAmber ♡
snippet.description:
Fans from all around the world wanted to show their support to lovely and talented Amber Laura Heard. This video is full of love and kindness. Here’s a special thank you to the amazing Alexia who made this beautiful video and to everyone who participated in this project.

Amber, we love you so much. You are so beautiful, talented, important and wonderful. We will always love and support you.

All my love,
Sara (@amberheardteam) ♡


*
Edited by: Alexia (@aheardonline)
